  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTraits_ctl00_LabelName\"><strong>Requirements</strong></span></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl04_LabelType\">Any elemental lord</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl04_LabelType\">Add 1 to the DC of saving throws made to resist the effects of spells cast by you that have either the air, earth, fire, or water descriptor, depending on which elemental lord you worship. You must choose a single elemental lord when you take this trait; once chosen, it cannot be changed.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Notes</strong></p>\n<p>This trait has the exact same function as <em>Affintiy of the Elements</em> from <em>Faiths of Corruption</em> <em>pg. 19</em>, but with slightly different wording.</p>",
